{"tid":1910841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：真好。香港電台捆綁銷售幾十年的合約期滿了。","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T22:33:41.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a14f62af940e80df8fd6f7789cdf048e2a42b8cc","tid":1910841,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"陳雲：真好。香港電台捆綁銷售幾十年的合約期滿了。<br />\n論香港電台。香港電台捆綁無線電視及亞視銷售幾十年的合約期滿了。<br />\n港台其實可以收檔。電視是講究整套生態的，TVB賤格仆街親共之後，拖累香港人不看電視，港台難以獨善其身。<br />\n現在脫離捆綁播出，是港台與TVB分開睡棺材，費事逼埋一齊下葬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8NkVgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8NkVgG.png&h=34976a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptVFVg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptVFVg4.png&h=d8357234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ebcf52b28c49f88d448f121482675a5825a39e0","tid":1910841,"uid":20170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"閱讀智力門檻：0"},{"pid":"a76e79362dd16ea647ecdcb19419be0bbbe4c18f","tid":1910841,"uid":3465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ebcf52b28c49f88d448f121482675a5825a39e0","tid":1910841,"uid":20170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"閱讀智力門檻：0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"閱讀智力上限：10"},{"pid":"f08e28ad05e9c2a28f7f552ea29d5b4cd801be28","tid":1910841,"uid":189243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:11:00.000Z","msg":"佢幾時先肯返青山覆診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e751e26ffbc7e7407c2a49990be9d374c0f7af","tid":1910841,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"今次有食藥"},{"pid":"cb9208b8217ff8f131a799cd520d6e3ec81dbca8","tid":1910841,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"熱血時報某d節目好過港台係